      <link>https://www.vxworks7.com/news/multiple-high-risk-vulnerability-alerts-for-vxworks/</link>
      <pubDate>Thu, 01 Aug 2019 23:06:00 +0800</pubDate>
      
      <guid>https://www.vxworks7.com/news/multiple-high-risk-vulnerability-alerts-for-vxworks/</guid>
      <description>&lt;h2 class=&#34;relative group&#34;&gt;背景 
    &lt;div id=&#34;%E8%83%8C%E6%99%AF&#34; class=&#34;anchor&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
    
    &lt;span
        class=&#34;absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 ltr:-left-6 rtl:-right-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100&#34;&gt;
        &lt;a class=&#34;group-hover:text-primary-300 dark:group-hover:text-neutral-700&#34;
